---
This software implements the BB84 quantum key distribution protocol
as described in:

  Bennett, C.H. and Brassard, G. "Quantum cryptography: Public key
  distribution and coin tossing." Theoretical Computer Science,
  vol. 560, pp. 7-11, 2014. (Original: Proc. IEEE ICCSP, 1984.)
  arXiv:2003.06557

and the Cascade error reconciliation protocol described in:

  Brassard, G. and Salvail, L. "Secret-Key Reconciliation by Public
  Discussion." EUROCRYPT 1993, LNCS 765, pp. 410-423.

The protocol designs are the intellectual work of their respective
authors. This implementation is original work by H. Overman.
